            <div class="faq-grid">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4>How far in advance should I book?</h4>
                    <p>We recommend booking at least 24 hours in advance, but we can accommodate same-day bookings subject to availability.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4>Do you provide child seats?</h4>
                    <p>Yes, we provide complimentary child seats and booster seats. Please specify your requirements when booking.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4>What if my flight is delayed?</h4>
                    <p>We monitor all flights and adjust pickup times automatically. There's no extra charge for flight delays.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4>Can I cancel or modify my booking?</h4>
                    <p>Yes, you can cancel or modify your booking free of charge up to 24 hours before the scheduled pickup time.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4>What payment methods do you accept?</h4>
                    <p>We accept cash, all major credit/debit cards, bank transfers, and PayPal. Corporate accounts are also available.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4>Are your drivers licensed?</h4>
                    <p>Yes, all our chauffeurs are fully licensed private hire drivers with enhanced DBS checks and extensive experience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
